\c 5
\s Ananiasi naSafira
\p
\v 1 Asi mumwe murume, wainzi Ananiasi, wakatengesa fuma yake anaSafira mukadzi wake,
\v 2 akasara nemumwe mugove pamutengo, mukadzi wake achizvizivavo, akavuya nomumwe mugove, ndokuuisa patsoka dzavapositora.
\v 3 Asi Peturo akati: Ananiasi, Satani wazadzireiko moyo wako, kuti unyengere Mweya Mutsvene, nokuzvikamurira zvomutengo womunda?
\v 4 Iwo uchiripo, wakanga usi wako here? Watengeswa, wakanga usi musimba nazvo here? Nemhaka yeiko waisa mumoyo mako chinhu ichi? Hauna kureva nhema kuvanhu, asi kunaMwari.
\v 5 Ananiasi, wakati achinzwa mashoko iwayo, akawira pasi, akabudisa mweya; kutya kukuru kukawira vose vakazvinzwa.
\v 6 Majaya akasimuka akamuputira ndokumutakurira kunze ndokumuviga.
\v 7 Nguva dzinege senhatu dzakati dzapfuvura, mukadzi wake akapinda asingazivi zvaitwa.
\v 8 Peturo akapindura, akati: Ndivudze kana makatengesa munda nemari yakadai? Iye akati: Hongu, neyakadai.
\v 9 Peturo akati kwaari: Maita seiko zvamarangana kuidza Mweya waShe? Tarira, tsoka dzavaviga murume wako, pamukova, vachakutakuriravo kunze.
\v 10 Ipapo akawira pasi pakarepo patsoka dzake, akabudisa mweya; majaya akapinda, akamuwana afa, ndokumutakurira kunze, ndokumuviga kumurume wake.
\v 11 Kutya kukuru kukawira kereke yose navose vakanzwa zvinhu izvi.
\v 12 Uye namaoko avapositora kwakaitwa zviratidzo nezvinoshamisa zvizhinji zvakaitwa pakati pavanhu; vose vaiva nomoyo mumwe pabiravira raSoromoni.
\v 13 Asi pakati pavamwe kwakanga kusinomunhu wakatsunga kuzvisanganisa kwavari; asi vanhu vaivakudza zvikuru
\v 14 Vatendi vakawedzerwa vakawanda kwazvo kunaIshe zvaunga zviviri vakadzi navarume, varume navakadzi, vairamba vachiwedzerwa kunaShe.
\v 15 Kusvikira vatakurira varwere munzira dzomumusha, vakaradzika pamibhedha napanhovo, kuti mumvuri waPeturo achipfuura ufukidze umwe wavo.
\v 16 Uye kwakauyawo chaunga chemaguta akapoteredza Jerusarema, vachivuya navarwere, navaitambudzwa nemweya yetsvina, vakaporeswa vose.
\s vapositora vanobudiswa mutirongo
\p
\v 17 Zvino muprista mukuru akasimuka, navose vaiva naye vaiva vechikamu chevaSajusi, vanegodo kwazvo;
\v 18 vakabata vapositora vakavaisa mutirongo maipinzwa vanhu vose.
\v 19 Asi mutumwa waShe wakazarura mikova yetirongo vusiku akavabudisa akati:
\v 20 Endai, mumire muchitaura mutembere kuvanhu mashoko ose ovupenyu ubwu.
\v 21 Vakati vachinzwa, vakapinda mutembere mangwanani, vakadzidzisa. Zvino muprista mukuru akasvika navaiva naye, vakakokera makurukota nevungano yose yavakuru vavana vaIsraeri; vakatumira \add vanhu\add* kutirongo kuti vavuye navo.
\v 22 Asi varanda vakati vachisvikapo, vakawana vasimo mutirongo; vakadzoka, vakavavudza izvozvo,
\v 23 tvachiti irongo zvirokwazvo takaiwana yakazarirwa zvakasimba kwazvo, navarindi vamire panze pamikova; asi tati tichizarura, tikasawana munhu mukati.
\v 24 Zvino Muprista nomukuru wetembere navaprista vakuru vakati vachinzwa mashoko iwayo, vakakahadzika pamusoro pazvo, vasingazivi kuti zvinozodini.
\v 25 Ipapo mumwe munhu akasvika akavavudza achiti: Tarirai, varume vamakaisa mutirongo, vamire mutembere, vachidzidzisa vanhu.
\v 26 Zvino mutungamiriri wavarwi, navatariri, vakaenda, vakavuya navo, vasingaiti nesimba, nokuti vakanga vachitya vanhu kuti vangatakwa namabwe.
\v 27 Vakati vasvika navo, vakavaisa kumakurukota. Muprista mukuru akavabvunza
\v 28 achiti: Ko hatina kukurairai zvikuru kuti murege kudzidzisa nezita iri here?, zvino tarirai, mazadza Jerusarema nokudzidzisa kwenyu; muchida kuti ropa romunhu uyu rivuye pamusoro pedu.
\v 29 Zvino Peturo navapositora vakapindura vakati: Tinofanira kuteerera Mwari kupfuvura vanhu.
\v 30 Mwari wamadzibaba edu wakamutsa Jesu iye wamakavuraya muchimuturika pamuti,
\v 31 Mwari wakamusimudza iye noruvoko rwake rworudyi, ave Mutungamiriri noMusununguri, kuti ape vaIsraeri kutendevuka nekangamwiro yezvivi.
\v 32 Isu tiri zvapupu zvamashoko iwayo; noMweya Mutsvenevo, wavakapiwa naMwari ivo vanomuteerera.
\v 33 Zvino ivo vakati vachizvinzwa, vakafa neshungu, vakada kuvavuraya.
\v 34 Ipapo mumwe muFarisi, wainzi Gamarieri, mudzidzisi womurairo, waikudzwa navanhu vose, akasimuka pamakurukota, akaraira kuti vapositora vabudiswe chinguva chiduku;
\v 35 akati kwavari: Varume vaIsraeri, chenjerai zvamunoda kuitira vanhu ava.
\v 36 Nokuti kare kwakambomuka Tudasi, achiti, ndiri munhu mukuru, vanhu vanenge mazana mana vakamutevera; iye akavurawa, navose vaimuteerera vakaparadzirwa, nokuparadzwa.
\v 37 Shure komunhu uyu Judhasi weGariri akamuka, pamazuva okuverengwa, akatsausa vanhu kuti vamutevere; iye akaparara, navose vakamuteerera, vakaparadzirwa.
\v 38 Zvino ndinoti kwamuri: Musabata vanhu ava, muvarege, nokuti kana kufunga uku nebasa iri zviri zvavanhu, zvichaparadzwa.
\v 39 Asi kana zviri zvaMwari, hamungagoni kuzviparadza; kuti zvimwe mungadai muchirwa naMwarivo.
\v 40 Vakamunzwa; ipapo vakati vadana vapositora, vakavarova, vakavaraira kuti varege kutaura nezita raJesu; vakavaregedza.
\v 41 Ipapo vakabuda pamakurukota, vachifara, zvavakanzi vakafanirwa kunyadziswa nokuda kwezita rake.
\v 42 Havana kurega kudzidzisa, nokuparidza mazuva ose zvaKristu Jesu, mutembere kana kudzimba dzavo.
